channel.title: NOT EXISTING ITEM error
channel.description:
So I get on my wildscape blank source and client and get on teh pvserver custom p4ck v3 and put in admin goddsword. I did everything and it worked. But, when I put it on my player, it still has the sprite and I'm still wearing it, but in combat style I get NOT EXISTING ITEM and no stats, but I put stats in item.cfg.
Help?

item.title: NOT EXISTING ITEM error
item.dc:creator: @arham_4 arham 4
item.description:
@arham_4 wrote:

[quote=“13lack drag, post:2, topic:386382”]Most sources will work, but this is what you do.

  1. Find Item.cfg
  2. At the very bottom, Not after, but before

    [ENDOFITEMLIST]

    put this

Explaind: [quote]item = youritemid[/quote] specifies what item you are talking about.
[quote]Your_item_name[/quote] replaces the Non existing item note: you must have underscpres
p is a place gholder, i think. the 1st 3 numbers are 1) Buy price 2) low alch price 3) high alch price#'s 4,5,6,7,8, Attacking stats #'s 9,10,22,12,13, Defense stats #'s 14,15, Str bonus, and pray bonus
Ummm,[/quote][quote=“arham 4, post:1, topic:386382”]but I put stats and everything in item.cfg.[/quote]
